title: Logan Square 2 Bed 1 Bath September 1 Parking Available
posting_body: ['Contact info:', 'Patty or Miguel | 312-656-4600', 'Logan Square Unit #1 2 Bed 1 Bath Available September  1', '2259 W Diversey Ave #1, Chicago, IL 60647', '$2,150/mo', 'DESCRIPTION', 'Condo quality, 1st floor, 2 bedroom 1 bath unit for rent 2 flat.', 'Features include prewired TV wall hookups in bedrooms, bathroom and living room.', 'Hardwood floors, recessed lighting, ceiling fans, lots of natural light, sun room, and glass shower enclosure.', 'Eat in kitchen including dishwasher.', 'Custom closet systems and private back porch area and Juliet balcony.', 'Private back yard.', 'Laundry is in common Area.', 'Located walking distance from River walk, Logan Square farmers market, Midtown Athletic Club, Xsport, Petsmart, Target, Costco, Fresh Thyme, HomeGoods, and restaurants.', 'Centrally located between CTA bus and train routes and Interstate 90/94.', 'Owner pays for trash, water, sewer and water.', 'Tenant responsible for gas and electric.', 'Parking available for additional cost.', '  *Absolutely No Solicitors*  Please watch our Virtual Tour:  https://youtu.be/-c3LrzQSH1Q', 'RENTAL FEATURES', 'Living room', 'Dining room', 'Master bath', 'Family room', 'Breakfast nook', 'Office', 'Sun room', 'Range / Oven', 'Refrigerator', 'Dishwasher', 'Microwave', 'Stainless steel appliances', 'Freezer', 'Balcony, Deck, or Patio', 'Yard', 'Fenced yard', 'Lawn', 'Heat: forced air', 'Ceiling fans', 'Double pane / Storm windows', 'Cable-ready', 'Hardwood floor', 'Granite countertop', 'Industrial Front Load Washer & Dryer', 'COMMUNITY FEATURES', 'Vintage building', 'Secured entry', 'There are 2 indoor parking spots available at an additional cost.', 'Garage - Attached', 'Contact info:', 'Miguel or Pat', '773-851-2475', 'Please watch our Virtual Tour:  https://youtu.be/-c3LrzQSH1Q']
